tupakihi
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:  1
Definition:[Ma.] a native plant, tutu of the Coriaria spp.
Origin: [none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain: Rural
Region: [none]
